data.description: CALLING ALL INVESTORS!!! This gigantic 3 story home in Old Louisville has many of its original features including 2 glorious original staircases, 11 fireplaces, original hardwoods & woodwork throughout, 3 sets of original pocket doors, 6 huge bedrooms & 3 full bathrooms. This grand home has all the lovely features you would expect in a 130yr old home in Old Louisville. This home needs some TLC and repairs, therefore, it is being offered AS-IS and seller is unable to make any repairs. This home has been strategically priced to reflect needed repairs. Bring your creative design ideas & bring this home back to its glory! This property may be eligible for a Conventional 203K loan, allowing you to finance the rehab cost.
